name: Jet Alone [Prototype V2]
description:
For my second game prototype I wanted to expand my first iteration of a helicopter style game. I wanted to use this project to help myself learn to sculpt an open level to fly around in. I had some fun deciding how the level would look and would items to place down. 

There is a chance I may expand on this prototype and flesh it out. I would create various levels and fun enemies to fight against.
